got you in my line of sight.

60
00:07:51,384 --> 00:07:52,849
- Mr. Jake.
- Mr. Gundersen.

61
00:07:52,884 --> 00:07:54,052
Yeah. Please, sir?

62
00:07:54,086 --> 00:07:55,722
I hope nothing is
wrong with your order.

63
